  <title>Display a data value's audit trail</title>
  <para>
    <screenshot>
      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata width="40%" align="center"
            fileref="resources/images/data_entry/data_entry_audit_trail.png" format="PNG"/>
        </imageobject>
      </mediaobject>
    </screenshot>
  </para>
  <para>The audit trail allows you to view other data values which have been entered prior to the
    current value. The audit trail also shows when the data value was altered and which user who
    made the changes.</para>
  <orderedlist>
    <listitem>
      <para>Open the <emphasis role="bold">Data Entry</emphasis> app.</para>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <para>Open an existing data entry form.</para>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <para>Double-click the field with the value you want to view the audit trail for.</para>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <para>Click <emphasis role="bold">Audit trail</emphasis>.</para>
    </listitem>
  </orderedlist>
</section>
